      "algorithm": "Example: Binary Search (Divide & Conquer)\n\n1. Start with a sorted list.\n2. Pick the middle item.\n3. Match? You found it! Stop.\n4. Too big? Discard the right half.\n5. Too small? Discard the left half.\n6. Repeat until found or empty.",
